ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office, Alone
ResponseRule.description: Player has returned to his office for the first time since rescuing Mikhaila. Only Mikhaila is alive.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + January
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's talking to January when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until Morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + January Interrupted
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's talking to January when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until Morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + Igwe
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's talking to Igwe when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until Morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + Igwe Interrupted
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's is talking to Igwe when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + Igwe + January
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's talking to Igwe and January when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until Morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: 1st Arrival In Office + Igwe + January Interrupted
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is talking to Igwe and January when Morgan shows up at the office. They'll keep talking until the end of the convo or until morgan interrupts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Subsequent Visit, Reward
ResponseRule.description: Player has returned to his office for the first time in a while, Mikhaila has more rewards.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila:Overheard Convo w/ Igwe -- Russian Volunteers
ResponseRule.description: Player has returned to his office. Pre-Apex. This should occur after the Volunteer revelations (Whistleblower Quest).

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila:Overheard Convo w/ January -- Morgan Memory Loss
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila and January (Maybe Igwe) talk about Morgan's memory loss.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Overheard Convo w/ Igwe -- Morgan Memory Loss
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila and Igwe talk about Morgan's memory loss. In case January is dead.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Finding My Father Intro
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office and explains her true purpose on the station: finding her father. Convo branches potentially, if the player has already completed elements.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Finding My Father -- Give Whistle Blower
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office and explains her true purpose on the station: finding her father. Play this line if the player hasn't started Whistle Blower objective.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Finding My Father -- Whistleblower In Progress
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office and explains her true purpose on the station: finding her father. Play this line if the player already started Whistle Blower quest, but hasn't completed it.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Finding My Father -- Give Missing Father
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office and explains her true purpose on the station: finding her father. Play this if the player has already completed whistleblower.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila's Father. Erased Archive.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Player returns to office after having completed the Mikhaila's Father Object, BUT the player deleted the archive. Mikhaila will likely never know what happened to her father.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Mikhaila's Father. Transferred Archive. Waiting.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Player returns to office after having completed the Mikhaila's Father Object, and the player transferred the archive to his machine. Mikhaila and Morgan can listen to the audiolog together. She's waiting for player to press the button.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila's Father. Transferred Archive. Loiter.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Player returns to office after having completed the Mikhaila's Father Object, and the player transferred the archive to his machine. Mikhaila and Morgan can listen to the audiolog together. MIkhaila reminds the player to get on with it.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila's Father. Reaction after hearing Archive.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Reaction after hearing her father die in an experiment. Also reacts to the fact that Morgan's voice was in the recording.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila's Father. Reaction after hearing Archive + Igwe + January
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Reaction after hearing her father die in an experiment. Also reacts to the fact that Morgan's voice was in the recording. This variation has Igwe and January lines.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila's Father. Player Delete Archive In Her Face
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is in Morgan's office. Player Deletes Father's Log in Office in Front of Her, gets furious with player.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, While Father Quest Active
ResponseRule.description: After Mikhaila explains her true purpose on the station and gives the player her side quest. Follow up lines.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, After Listening to Log w/ Morgan, Just After
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments just after hearing the log. pissed.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, After Listening to Log w/ Morgan, Just After. Leave.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments just after hearing the log. pissed. last comment.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, After Listening to Log w/ Morgan, Forgiven.
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after her side quest is resolved.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, After Deleting Log In Her Face, Pt1
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after the playe deleted the log in front of her face.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, After Deleting Log In Her Face, Pt2
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after the playe deleted the log in front of her face.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Dahl is Here
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after Dahl has arrived.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Player Destroyed Dahl's Operators
ResponseRule.description: Player defeated Dahls operators that were trying to hack their way into his office.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Dahl Is Ready For NM Removal. Igwe Gone.
ResponseRule.description: Igwe won't be in the Office, he leaves as soon as Dahl is subdued. This is the last thing Mikhaila will say in the office - if the player uninstalls the Neuromod, she should jump to the Shuttle Bay and will no longer be in the office. (There's a TranScribe indicating this.)

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Apex Is Here
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after the Apex has arrived. There's still hope of getting off the station with Dahl and the shuttle.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Apex Is Here, No Father Quest
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments after the Apex has arrived. There's still hope of getting off the station with Dahl and the shuttle.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Fallback Early Comments
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's is in the player's office. Player is just hanging around her. Early comments. Shouldn't play late game.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Player Has Both Keys. Blow it up!
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments if player returns to talk to her after he has both keys. She encourages him to blow stuff up. Won't play if teh TS version has already played.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Player Used Both Keys. Blow it up!
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments if player returns to talk to her after he has USED both keys. She encourages him to blow stuff up. Won't play if teh TS version has already played.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: ClickMe, Final Fare Well, Escape Pod, No Shuttle
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's comments if player returns to talk to her after he triggered the self destruct. There's no shuttle and the player is on the way to grab the scape pod.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Fallback Loiter Comments
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's is in the player's office. Player is just hanging around her.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Fallback Approach Greeting
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila's is in the player's office. Player is just hanging around her.

ResponseRule.description: This can play anywhere. Mikhaila sees the player use one of the alien powers.
